    <title>Graphs</title>
    <p>Graphs is a GNOME-Circle application for plotting and manipulating scientific data. Import datasets from files or databases, generate data from equations, apply mathematical operations, fit curves, and export publication-ready figures, all within
        a clean, native interface.</p>
    <p>Use the topics below to learn how to use Graphs.</p>
